description: As a user I should be able to test U1 Details Tab in CSR Portal.
name: U1 Details Tab Regression suite

elements.name: As a user, he/she should launch the application successfully

steps.name: User should launch the application
User enters UserName
User enters Password
User clicks on Login Button
User should see login message 'Logon successful'

elements.name: User should be able to search for a policy

steps.name: User enters a policy
User clicks on Search Button
User should be able to see CSR Policy Page 'Customer service Portal - Policy '

elements.name: User should be able to Authorize the call

steps.name: User clicks on authorize button
Policy Number should reflect in authorize label
Full Name should reflect in authorize label
Authorized Role should reflect in authorize label
Authorized Full Name should reflect in Notes tab
Authorized Role should reflect in Notes label

elements.name: User should be able to check Policy Details checkbox

steps.name: User checks the checkboxes they should reflect in Requested Details and user should be able to close the call

elements.name: User should be able to see the authorized Time in My call History Widget

steps.name: User should see the time in My Call History Widget
